
1   Ng'olyootap Kamuktaindet ne Toroor ne ki nyoonji Mikah meng'iindetap Moresheth eng' peetuusyegap Jotham, Ahaz, ak Hezekiah, laitorinigap Judah, ne ki keer agobo Samaria ak Jerusalem.

Maonatosyek agobo kirwooget


2  Ogas okweek pororyosyek, okweek tugul, oepchi iit, ee ng'wony, ak tugul che mi olooto: ak ingoek Kiptaiyat Kamuktaindet ne Toroor paoryat eng' okweek, Kiptaiyat ne mi hekalunnyi ne tiliil. 
3  Amu, ogeero, mong'u Kamuktaindet ne Toroor eng' oldanyi, ak kochoorgei, ak kotyech komoswek che torooreen che po ng'wony. 
4  Ak kochootyo tuloonook eng' keelyekyik, ak kobetogis atebwosyek, ko uu ye chotei temeniet ko kauchi maat, ko uu peek che kirandoi eng' ole keigei. 
5  Piitu chuuto amu pistoetap Jakobo, ak amu tengekwogigap kootap Israel. Nee pistoetap Jakobo? Tos ma Samaria? Ak nee komoswek che torooreen che po Judah? Tos ma Jerusalem? 
6  Ayae anyun Samaria koek karurugutyetap emet, ak koigei ole kiminjin sabibuk: ak atumde koikyik koba atebweet, ak ang'aany lumeiywekyik. 
7  Ak kebir ketuatui kanamonikyik tugul che ki kiwai, ak kebeel melekwekyik tugul, ak ang'em kanamonikyik tugul: amu ki iyumune chooto melektap kugoinatet, ak koweekyigei melektap kugoinatet.


8  Ateei ak awaache amu niito, awendi ko kagireegunena ngoroik ak ami aach ngor: ateei ko uu lelwek, ak ariire ko uu tyong'igap songolik. 
9  Amu ma inyaaksei mookyik; amu kagonyo kot koit Judah; itei ormariichetap piikyuk, agoi Jerusalem. 
10  Amat imwaite ng'olyoondoniito eng' Gath, amat iriir agot kitigin: ki amildaegei temburyek eng' Beth-le-Apra. 
11  Osiirte, ee okweek piik che omenye Sapir, osiirte omi aach ngor ak kalilanet: tomo komong' chiito ne menyei Saanan; rebenok kateiyetap Beth-esel kinnyi ne tonone. 
12  Amu igeni miising' chiito ne menyei Marot kole konyoor myeeindo: amu kachoorchigei yaityet ormariichetap Jerusalem kobunu Kamuktaindet ne Toroor. 
13  Ratyi chepkichutitap lugeet paraisiit ne chepchep, ee inyee chiito ne imenye Lakish: kitaunindetap tengekto ineendet ne po cheptap Zion; amu ki kinyoorchin pistaosyegap Israel. 
14  Igoochini anyun Moreset-gat kagoochinetap saisere: egu kooriigap Aksip kiit ne po ng'aalseet eng' laitorinigap Israel. 
15  Ta amutun chiito ne nyoonei konamin ibunji, ee inyee ne imenye Maresha: itei toroornatetap Israel Adulam. 
16  Ingochurin met, ak icheru meting'ung' agobo lagok che iboiboin: tes poostong'ung' si koigei ne po chepsengwet; amu kageluul icheek eng' ole imi.

